define({"topics":[{"title":"Translation memories ","shortdesc":"<p class=\"shortdesc\">TMs are the most important of all translation resources so it's important to choose a         TMS that has the most options to manage them easily.<\/p>","href":"topics\/tm_management.html","attributes":{"data-id":"tm_management"},"menu":{"hasChildren":false},"tocID":"tm_management-d599e342","topics":[]},{"title":"Alignment","shortdesc":"<p class=\"shortdesc\">While alignment is a feature shared with a lot of CAT tools, its use can vary from         very difficult to extremely easy so you should choose your TMS carefully.<\/p>","href":"topics\/alignment.html","attributes":{"data-id":"alignment"},"menu":{"hasChildren":false},"tocID":"alignment-d599e353","topics":[]},{"title":"Termbases","shortdesc":"<p class=\"shortdesc\">Using a termbase is an excellent solution for terminology management. TMSs should         have relevant features to make your work easier and quicker.<\/p>","href":"topics\/term_bases.html","attributes":{"data-id":"term_bases"},"menu":{"hasChildren":false},"tocID":"term_bases-d599e364","topics":[]},{"title":"Terminology extraction","shortdesc":"<p class=\"shortdesc\">Computer-aided terminology extraction proves useful when you need to search for         customer-specific vocabulary.<\/p>","href":"topics\/terminology_extraction.html","attributes":{"data-id":"terinology_extraction"},"menu":{"hasChildren":false},"tocID":"terinology_extraction-d599e375","topics":[]},{"title":"Concordance","shortdesc":"<p class=\"shortdesc\">Context is the king in translation. Here is how Concordance helps linguists make the         most of translation resources in XTM.<\/p>","href":"topics\/concordance.html","attributes":{"data-id":"concordance"},"menu":{"hasChildren":false},"tocID":"concordance-d599e386","topics":[]},{"title":"Language variants","shortdesc":"<p class=\"shortdesc\">Some languages have variants that you want to preserve in separate translation         memories. However, a problem appears if you want to leverage on cost reductions due to a         high number of matches from a <a class=\"xref\" href=\"glossary\/r_glossary.html#g_translation_memory\">TM<\/a>         with a different language variant.<\/p>","href":"topics\/language_variants.html","attributes":{"data-id":"language_variants"},"menu":{"hasChildren":false},"tocID":"language_variants-d599e397","topics":[]}]});